年初突然宣布，关停所有电动车生产线；通用汽车则推迟了新工厂的开设计划。近日，苹果公司放弃了坚持10年的造车项目，也引发了“当前已不是造电动车的好时机”的议论。 一夜之间，电动车从人人争抢的“香饽饽”，变成了“烫手山芋”。国际车企纷纷推迟甚至关闭电动车业务。似乎只有中国车企还在坚持。回顾过去十多年，电动车在全球市场经历了高速发展的黄金时期，电动化也一度成为全球汽车业的共识。如今，一场前所未有的“逆流”出现了。欧美车企掀电动车“逆流” 中国恐成“电动车孤岛”？"},"attached_info":"CkAIt/u3iarSiYcgEAMaCTEwNjI4MzY4MCC9wbqvBjAAOPACQAFyCTY0ODAyOTE4MngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"988 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-f65dd27c8d1eec3ba8256f439ca2c303_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"2_1710170213.566693","card_id":"Q_646724300","target":{"id":646724300,"title":"普通人不要盲目挑战麦当娜 16 连蹲，连续深蹲的安全隐患有哪些？该如何避免？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/646724300","type":"question","created":1709349400,"answer_count":65,"follower_count":135,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[833,39355,46547,167456,270343],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"#普通人不要盲目挑战麦当娜16连蹲 近日，麦当娜曾在演唱会上连做16个深蹲跳起的视频忽然爆火网络，引起多人跟风挑战。在此提示：连续深蹲跳起会对心肺产生巨大压力，同时对身体体能和协调性都有较高要求，盲目跟风可能会给身体造成损伤。"},"attached_info":"CkAIt/u3iarSiYcgEAMaCTEwNTk5NDIzMiCYtIqvBjAAOIcBQAJyCTY0NjcyNDMwMHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"738 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-646c841aef2e2026e9ed5e60800f3ddd_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"3_1710170213.568670","card_id":"Q_648056180","target":{"id":648056180,"title":"空军副司令表示「轰-20将很快正式公布」，哪些信息值得关注？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/648056180","type":"question","created":1710144578,"answer_count":198,"follower_count":592,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[1234,20609,21202,160300,2355460],"comment_count":